<p>
<note n="0371003" resp="#resp3" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0371003">「牙」，底本不清，似作「芽」，據北新627號錄文。</note>
<note n="0371004" resp="#resp3" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0371004">「勝」，底本作「朦」，據北新627號改。</note>
<note n="0372001" resp="#resp3" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0372001">「經」，底本無，據北新627號補。</note>
<note n="0372002" resp="#resp3" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0372002">「靈」，底本無，據北新627號補。</note>
<note n="0372003" resp="#resp3" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0372003">「壁」，底本作「譬」，據文意改。</note>
</p>
